1505	**Rolling Deploy Procedure**:
1506	```
1507	1. Pre-deploy checks:
1508	   - Run full test suite (CI gate)
1509	   - Verify migration is backward-compatible (no column drops/renames without expand phase)
1510	   - Tag release: v5.1.0-p{N}
1511	
1512	2. Database migration (before code deploy):
1513	   - Run additive migrations only (ADD COLUMN, CREATE INDEX)
1514	   - Use `php artisan migrate --pretend` first to preview
1515	   - Monitor lock wait time during migration
1516	
1517	3. App deploy (rolling, one node at a time):
1518	   a. Drain node from load balancer
1519	   b. Deploy code
1520	   c. php artisan config:cache && php artisan route:cache && php artisan view:cache
1521	   d. php artisan optimize
1522	   e. Readiness check: curl http://localhost:8002/api/v5/readyz → 200
1523	   f. Re-add to load balancer
1524	   g. Wait 30s, verify error rate stable
1525	   h. Proceed to next node
1526	
1527	4. Queue worker restart:
1528	   a. php artisan horizon:pause (or supervisor signal QUIT for graceful drain)
1529	   b. Wait for in-flight jobs to complete (max 120s)
1530	   c. Deploy code
1531	   d. php artisan horizon:continue
1532	
1533	5. Post-deploy verification:
1534	   - Monitor Sentry for 5xx spike (5 min window)
1535	   - Check p95 latency vs SLO
