1716	**2. Single-Flight Locking** (prevent stampede):
1717	```php
1718	public function remember(array $tags, string $key, int $ttl, Closure $callback): mixed
1719	{
1720	    // ... existing CacheService logic ...
1721	    $lock = Cache::lock("lock:{$key}", 10); // 10s max wait
1722	    if ($lock->get()) {
1723	        try {
1724	            $value = $callback();
1725	            // store in cache...
1726	            return $value;
1727	        } finally {
1728	            $lock->release();
1729	        }
1730	    }
